comments:
The alien words go in pairs. The alien words have the same symbols at the end position but a different symbol in the second position. I paired the pictures that had the same symbol at the end and the second position, the symbols looked like a fish drawing, 1 is looking to the left while the other is facing up. Thats how i differentiated them.
The beginning of the task was very difficult. I was trying to find a pattern which took time but once i found it, it back simpler. Also, the second part of the task was difficult, the words were moving quickly but once i identified the symbol at the end, i tried guessing which picture to pick
